<br>
I followed the directions here and got 2 instant port items, I Leatherfoot Raiders Skullcap and a Lizard blood potion.  After 3 Wizards, I finally found one willing to give it a try.  The instant port potion for him made the difference in swaying his decision.   I banked all my stuff, met the wizard in WC, got my guild to buffs us to bursting and ported up.   I zoned in and saw the wizard argo'd and porting out.  I quickly sneak/hid and made my way to the east wall.  I saw a rat and the golem in the port in room but that was it.  I made my way down the east wall to the turn west point.  Never saw a thing.  Got liche casting messages though. <br>
<br>
Next, I went west to the fountain and paused to spin around. Nothing!  About then I got the message &quot;You start to HATE this place&quot;, hehe.  Procedded into maestro's hall, met a ghoul, con'd indif.  turned sharp right, ran up stairs hugging the inside. Still getting casting messages, no argo that I could tell.  headed upstairs, clear as far as I could see.  Headed to the bed, no mobs, NO BOOK!!!  sigh.  so I hugged the wall south of the book facing the bed and camped.<br>
<br>
Hope I can camp in and invis before any mobs will argo.  Hope the book is there.<br>
<br>
I assume there must have been a hate raid earlier in the day, hence the lack of mobs?<br>
<br>
well, now to wait <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uorlun2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>orlun2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/1/01 2:16:24 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Get your Book of Souls - solo</span><hr size=1> Success! - waited 8 hours while playing alt's and trying to do a /who all of just about everyone to see if any hate raids where starting.  Logged back in beside the table, picked the book up, clicked my port potion and...done!<br>
